data.description: Discover your dream home in Kissimmee's Remington subdivision. Beautiful freshly painted  4-bedroom, 2-bath home. This gem offers cathedral ceilings, insulated windows, and a stunning pond view at the rear. Located in a gated community and close to stores, it's a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. This is an ideal space for families, professionals, and anyone seeking a place to call their own in the heart of Kissimmee. Just got a fresh coat of paint. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Remington gem your new home.
